1. ansible-vault create playbook.yml           --->>> Creates an encrypted yaml file
2. ansible-vault edit playbook.yml             --->>> To edit an encrypted yaml file
3. ansible-vault encrypt playbook.yml          --->>> To encrypt an unencrypted yaml file.
4. ansible-vault decrypt playbook.yml          --->>> To decrypt an encrypted yaml file.
5. ansible-vault rekey playbook                --->>> To change the vault password
6. --vault-id @ prompt                         --->>> This option prompts for the vault password
7. --vault-password-file=vault-file            --->>> To access the vault password from vault file

